{"type":null,"faqId":45533,"title":"荣耀小K手表换张SIM卡之后扫描二维码失败，无法配对成功怎么办？","answer":"<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">\n<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" id=\"softwareDescription\" jQuery17108353277590177472=\"16\">\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">手表更换<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡后，只需要使用之前的账号登陆华为穿戴<span lang=\"EN-US\">APP</span>，宝贝信息会自动更新为手表当前的<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡号，无需重新绑定配对。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>如果更换<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span></b><b>卡之后数据或通讯业务出现异常，请按如下步骤操作：</b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemList\"><span style=\"POSITION: relative; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; FONT-SIZE: 8pt; TOP: -1pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-text-raise: 1.0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">l<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>确认<span lang=\"EN-US\">APP</span>侧手表号码是否更新。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemListText\">打开华为穿戴<span lang=\"EN-US\">APP</span>，点击右上角人形图标，在头像旁边会显示手表号码，确认是否更新。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemList\"><span style=\"POSITION: relative; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; FONT-SIZE: 8pt; TOP: -1pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-text-raise: 1.0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">l<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>确认版本号，如果不是最新版本，请升级最新版本，重启手表，重新登陆<span lang=\"EN-US\">APP</span>再次尝试。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemListText\">如果已经为最新版本，告知用户注销重新登录<span lang=\"EN-US\">APP</span>、重启手表，信息同步可能需要一些时间，请耐心等待。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>如果用户一定要重新绑定：</b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemList\"><span style=\"POSITION: relative; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; FONT-SIZE: 8pt; TOP: -1pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-text-raise: 1.0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">l<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>需在数据业务正常的情况下，先接触绑定，然后才能再次绑定。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemList\"><span style=\"POSITION: relative; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; FONT-SIZE: 8pt; TOP: -1pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-text-raise: 1.0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">l<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡需开通【<span lang=\"EN-US\">2G</span>数据流量业务】、【短信业务】及【来电显示业务】。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemList\"><span style=\"POSITION: relative; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; FONT-SIZE: 8pt; TOP: -1pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-text-raise: 1.0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">l<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡需为实名办理。</p>\n<p class=\"ItemList\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1054","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442559368000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":79,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"K1-G01,荣耀小K,儿童手表,K1,二维码,扫描,配对失败,无法配对","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}